media:group.media:title: Security Booth - Who Goes There?
media:group.media:description:
Strange things happen on the night shift. In the security booth, it's our job to determine who gets access to this research facility. With seven endings, how will our decisions impact our fate?
Check out the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1828690/Security_Booth_Directors_Cut/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/aWa84VVcTA
